
  Harlequin

  A 64kb intro by Mewlers
  Contribution to the Plutonium 99 intro compo

  Requires

  Graphics adapter supporting lowres 16bpp modes and Univbe loaded
  Gravis Ultrasound for music (no SB sorry, maybe later)
  Should work with 32mb of memory (I guess :))
  A fast Pentium class processor is recommended

  Credits

  Rainmaker: Code, Design
  216: Vesa and memory control, optimizing
  Synteesi: Music
  Honeybunny: Design tips
  Uncle-x: Party animal

